{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC05_KEI_070.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1f,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Oh, it's Mr. Keith. I guess he's doing some researching here today."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Mr. Keeei‐"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "(Oops. I shouldn't talk to him when he's focused like that.)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "(I'll feel bad for interrupting him,<CR>so I should slooowly pass him by...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "(Slooowly, slooowwwly...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Why are you tiptoeing?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Hyah! I-I thought it was best not to interrupt you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "So I was trying to pass by you without you noticing me..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "That's surprisingly considerate of you. I'd appreciate it if you were always like that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "But fine, I've just reached a point where I can pause. If you have something to ask, I'll deal with it now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Actually, I don't have anything in particular that I wanted to ask you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Oh, but, I am interested in what you're doing here today!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Oh. While I was reading through the literature in the library, I ran into a few things I didn't know."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "So I came here to investigate.<CR>Sort of like a field study."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1ca,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "The ruins and brilliant flowers are extremely interesting to me as well."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "About the flowers? Have you been looking into finding Nio, too...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I do have somewhat of an interest in how you're going to resolve this case."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Even I don't know everything. The conclusion that you'll eventually reach..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1cf,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "I thought I'd come to it as well, in my own way."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Thank you so much! It's very reassuring to get your cooperation."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Don't misunderstand. I don't intend to do that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "To seek and to know comes as naturally to me as simply living."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Not to mention, there is no end to alchemy. No matter how far I go, it still won't mean that I've mastered it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "The truth is still far away. After coming to this land, I know that now more than ever."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1d0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "I have to continue to study without becoming too conceited."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "So it's even like that for Mr. Keith. Then I have much more to go..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "You're correct. You're only a chick that recently hatched from its egg."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "It's not a bad thing that you have such ambition. However, it's nothing more than a nuisance to me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Just keep devoting yourself. That'll probably lead you to saving your sister."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x15,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "I'll be going back now. Farewell."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "(I need to look to Mr. Keith's attitude as an example, and do my best...!)"
        }
    ]
}